The Worst Vacuum
Can I give negative starage??  Trust me.  It is VERY heavy, (& I am NOT a tiny woman), cumbersome & difficult to maneuver; the attchments fall off as I'm vacuuming, the flexible hose drags on the floor so I am actually able to run over it when I back up!  Also, a teensy, tiny bag that fills up really fast and then it will start spewing dust and dirt onto the floor.  I will never again trust Consumer Reports' recommendations and I cannot believe all of the glowing reviews for this machine.
      
